{"tid":1518991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派促市民明日831和理非表達訴求","createTime":"2019-08-30T12:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:06:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55e51c370f6c25842bbaf16ba3cfc22bad056fcc","tid":1518991,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477791-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477791-20190830.htm&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=06782775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477791-20190830.htm&h=bce49031\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477791-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣就人大8.31決定五周年發起明天遊行被警方反對，公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會今早亦駁回民陣上訴，民主派會議召集人毛孟靜說，民主派明日將會到街上陪同抗爭者，她強調民主派並沒有呼籲市民上街，但她希望市民明天盡量以「和理非」方式表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員范國威認為，警方對遊行申請發出反對通知書的做法，只會激發更多反對聲音，甚至可能將原本支持和理非的市民，也轉化成勇武抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，明日是「8.31」決定五周年，民主派將會去信中央，向國家主席習近平表明，行政長官林鄭月娥的管治方法已經不符合國家利益。"},{"pid":"8bcba20208dc1a9111aefd9d0a6a633f8f9a8321","tid":1518991,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:08:36.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyo